Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.30,0:00:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛馳的秒針 閃耀的流星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.07,0:00:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現代社會人心疲累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.71,0:00:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南的推理是一劑良藥喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.64,0:00:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的事件是銀行強盜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.39,0:00:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過卻有點詭異喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.43,0:00:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.12,0:00:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.09,0:00:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.14,0:00:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.58,0:01:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀行強盜殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.18,0:01:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 火雞耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.18,0:01:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}火雞:連續三次全中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.76,0:02:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.99,0:02:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周中時保齡球場上人也不多 真不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.49,0:02:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.44,0:02:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天剛好期中考試也結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.66,0:02:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.66,0:02:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 妳不是一直都很爽嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.55,0:02:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.88,0:02:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.05,0:02:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒有發燒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.35,0:02:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間倒是還早 不過還是回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.25,0:02:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.37,0:02:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.39,0:02:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘記去銀行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.02,0:02:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.94,0:02:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 爸爸有一張支付偵探費用的支票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.07,0:02:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我去銀行兌現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.15,0:02:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近有沒有銀行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.78,0:02:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個東都銀行在那邊拐角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.57,0:02:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉過去前面就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.81,0:02:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"東都銀行 米花公園北支行"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.93,0:02:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛好趕上了 小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.38,0:02:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就好了 等一下吧 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.66,0:03:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.72,0:03:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒還真是流行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.46,0:03:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.42,0:03:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是園子大小姐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.19,0:03:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有何貴幹哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.67,0:03:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是陪朋友來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.86,0:03:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.41,0:03:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請代我向令尊問好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.79,0:03:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子 那個人是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.73,0:03:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個支行的行長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.08,0:03:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是鈴木財團的大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.73,0:03:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.15,0:03:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是感冒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.95,0:03:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係吧 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.36,0:03:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咳嗽得挺厲害呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.34,0:03:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些喉糖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿意的話就拿去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.63,0:03:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.22,0:03:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太感謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.50,0:03:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.90,0:03:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷口先生 請過來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.85,0:03:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.86,0:04:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.95,0:04:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.91,0:04:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行長 那我出去辦事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.62,0:04:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.38,0:04:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都舉起手 原地站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.22,0:04:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 誰敢亂來馬上就沒命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.82,0:04:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.07,0:04:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒聽見嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.13,0:04:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是你們客戶存的錢嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.32,0:04:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這世上還真不公平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.08,0:04:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊那個男的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.67,0:04:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.94,0:04:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那些錢都裝到這裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.95,0:04:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於其他人 全給我站到櫃檯外邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.46,0:05:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 所有人都這樣乖乖地別動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.59,0:05:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 把錢都塞進包裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.49,0:05:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭 怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.74,0:05:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.95,0:05:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不輕舉妄動就不會有事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.54,0:06:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.92,0:06:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉…閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.36,0:06:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.68,0:06:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.41,0:06:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.26,0:06:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.52,0:06:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前島先生側腹中槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.66,0:06:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受了重傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.55,0:06:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但幸運的是並沒有生命危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.94,0:06:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.21,0:07:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前島先生正要用木刀襲擊的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.44,0:07:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在前島先生西裝口袋中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.80,0:07:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這隻手機卻響起來了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.56,0:07:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.49,0:07:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後搶匪回頭發現前島先生 就開了槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.01,0:07:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.59,0:07:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷口先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.23,0:07:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就飛撲到搶匪身上去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.72,0:07:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到前島中槍 女孩子們都在尖叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.11,0:07:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就覺得慌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.68,0:07:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶匪好像也很緊張 用手槍指著她們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.86,0:07:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一時間覺得情況危急 身體就不由自主地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.15,0:07:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我僅僅想要把槍口扳向其他方嚮而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.89,0:07:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻變成了這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.25,0:07:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.60,0:07:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑑定工作已經完成 可以進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.07,0:07:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位請在這裡稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.42,0:07:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手槍是用模型槍改裝而成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.71,0:08:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 防盜攝像機的錄影沒能顯示到這個區域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.60,0:08:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶匪身上也帶著手機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.17,0:08:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.23,0:08:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐伯通 昭和45年生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.57,0:08:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.23,0:08:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位有對犯人的相貌覺得眼熟的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.22,0:08:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.29,0:08:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是前島先生的手機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.73,0:08:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是警視廳的目暮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.68,0:08:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問您是哪位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.14,0:08:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小池先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.35,0:08:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是前島先生的客戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.58,0:09:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣 前島先生捲入了一件案子并且受了傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.56,0:09:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 請問您下午3點5分左右打過電話給這隻手機嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.48,0:09:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.61,0:09:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.46,0:09:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也讓我聽聽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.00,0:09:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案件發生的時候 你錄了音吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.82,0:09:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼大聲啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.16,0:09:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把錄音帶賣給媒體 好好地賺一筆呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.03,0:09:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.77,0:09:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就給你聽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.31,0:09:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准動 給我乖乖地待著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.84,0:09:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.04,0:09:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.21,0:09:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 整件案子的情況就可以大致掌握了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.78,0:09:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.49,0:09:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷口先生所做的構成犯罪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.78,0:09:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會 谷口先生如果沒有撲倒搶匪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.33,0:10:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶匪就有可能對你們開槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.73,0:10:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的行為 完全是不顧個人安危的英勇之舉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.38,0:10:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表揚都來不及 怎麼還會被判罪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.81,0:10:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.73,0:10:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 谷口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.60,0:10:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這么說 我們內部也一定要表揚你才行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.62,0:10:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.65,0:10:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是前島先生真不走運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.62,0:10:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道是誰打來的電話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.17,0:10:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有人湊巧給他的手機打那通電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.93,0:10:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說不定就不會被搶匪槍擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.50,0:10:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.62,0:10:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都弄錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.02,0:10:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.26,0:10:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行喔 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.95,0:11:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是很重要的東西 不可以拿來玩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.74,0:11:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷口先生 我們還需要你來做一下筆錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.07,0:11:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以請你到警署去一趟嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.88,0:11:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 我想去一下洗手間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.58,0:11:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.58,0:11:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.60,0:11:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上廁所嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.67,0:11:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.13,0:11:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷口先生為什麼匆忙地把手機收起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.41,0:11:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他剛才是要給什麼人打電話 還是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.21,0:11:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這件案子還有什麼隱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.62,0:11:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來你們竟然也遇上這件案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.92,0:11:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有受傷還真是萬幸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.44,0:12:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刷卡式的安全門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.08,0:12:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷口先生的西裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.15,0:12:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.40,0:12:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶匪似乎在找什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.26,0:12:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香煙 打火機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.60,0:12:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.04,0:12:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.90,0:12:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.68,0:12:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 搶匪在那之前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.25,0:12:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得就在這附近…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.88,0:12:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.72,0:12:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.27,0:12:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.85,0:13:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有意想不到的隱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.90,0:13:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然叔叔今天不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.92,0:13:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 只有再麻煩園子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.68,0:13:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.75,0:13:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.52,0:13:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇上這麼大的事 你一定也很疲憊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.56,0:13:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事 園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.24,0:13:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.32,0:13:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.30,0:13:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.45,0:13:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.32,0:13:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全都知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.84,0:13:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道什麼了 園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.99,0:13:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件案子背後可是有意想不到的內幕喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.03,0:13:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.67,0:13:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我是說有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.59,0:13:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模仿女生說話真難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.50,0:13:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說前島先生正要用木刀襲擊搶匪的時候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時響起來的根本不是前島先生的手機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.16,0:14:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是搶匪的手機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.63,0:14:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能 大家不是都證實當時是前島先生的手機響了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.63,0:14:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可剛才前島先生的手機響的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.98,0:14:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官先生和谷口先生不是也都弄錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而掏出了自己的手機嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.67,0:14:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與此相同地 大家那時也認為準是前島先生的手機響了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.24,0:14:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是有這種可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.75,0:14:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可妳怎麼知道就如妳所說的 是搶匪的手機響了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.95,0:14:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來電鈴聲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.50,0:14:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來電鈴聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.97,0:14:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將前島先生手機的來電鈴聲與搶匪的對比一聽就清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.77,0:14:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為案發當時響起的來電鈴聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.17,0:14:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經被那個學生用隨身聽錄在了磁帶上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.51,0:14:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 你有那種東西嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.98,0:14:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.95,0:14:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少給我胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.96,0:15:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊也沒用喔 我知道得清清楚楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.22,0:15:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 就是不肯協助調查嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.44,0:15:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 但是用完之後請務必還我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.29,0:15:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官 錄音機借來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.57,0:15:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.02,0:15:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.35,0:15:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是前島先生的手機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.48,0:15:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著是搶匪的手機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.67,0:15:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聲音相同 但節奏好像不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.74,0:15:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這是案發當時的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.71,0:15:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉…閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.98,0:15:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往前一點點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.57,0:15:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再回放一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.36,0:16:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個節奏的確是搶匪手機的來電鈴聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.01,0:16:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子 像妳所說的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.17,0:16:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案發當時響起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.99,0:16:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是搶匪的手機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.11,0:16:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有人正巧在那時打電話給搶匪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.86,0:16:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.90,0:16:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打電話來的恐怕是共犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.97,0:16:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.05,0:16:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那名共犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.40,0:16:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼看前島先生正要用木刀襲擊搶匪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.29,0:16:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就靈機一動 用帶在自己身上的手機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.25,0:16:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給搶匪打了一通電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.73,0:16:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.44,0:16:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.39,0:16:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.56,0:16:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那名共犯就在這些人之中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.62,0:16:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 那名共犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.91,0:16:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷口先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.11,0:16:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.18,0:16:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啊 請不要開玩笑好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.92,0:16:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷口先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.97,0:17:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先你用手機提示在銀行附近等待的搶匪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.39,0:17:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闖入銀行的時機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.35,0:17:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個行員專用出入口的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.72,0:17:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當有人外出時會從裡面打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.47,0:17:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但從外面沒有門卡是進不來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.41,0:17:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行長 那我出去辦事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.83,0:17:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.94,0:17:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下 我去把那邊的清單拿過來 妳先這樣繼續吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.41,0:17:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都舉起手 原地站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.52,0:17:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後 搶匪依照計劃吩咐你把錢塞進背包裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.30,0:17:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫃檯裡只留下你一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.59,0:17:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在想來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.71,0:17:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時搶匪根本就不往你邊看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.45,0:17:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按你的計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.88,0:17:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶匪本可以就這樣在不傷害任何人的情況下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.20,0:18:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你手中拿走裝滿錢的背包 然後逃之夭夭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.35,0:18:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後再碰頭平分贓款就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.42,0:18:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 中途卻發生了意想不到的變故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.33,0:18:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前島先生竟然恢復了意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.26,0:18:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要用某種方法提醒搶匪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.03,0:18:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本想大叫「小心後面」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.72,0:18:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可這樣就會被人識破你是共犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.79,0:18:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是你當時就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.42,0:18:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按下你手機的重撥鍵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.98,0:18:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實那時是搶匪的手機響了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.51,0:18:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但前島先生卻以為響的是他自己的手機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.62,0:18:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在停手的一刻中了槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.36,0:18:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說最大的失算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.11,0:18:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他竟然開槍打了前島先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.03,0:19:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚慌至極的搶匪失去自控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.31,0:19:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人也是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.85,0:19:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你判斷在這種情況下繼續執行計劃過於危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.73,0:19:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就向搶匪飛撲過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.40,0:19:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝作扭打引起手槍意外走火的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將搶匪殺人滅口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.56,0:19:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一派胡言 都是瞎編的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.56,0:19:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓我看看你的手機嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.44,0:19:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她說的是真相的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.25,0:19:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只要按下重撥鍵就應該會撥通搶匪的手機吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.65,0:19:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.30,0:19:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才在洗手間裡你已經把通話記錄刪除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.42,0:19:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官先生 我有他們二人是共犯的確切證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.21,0:19:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.24,0:19:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.65,0:19:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官先生 把兩手張開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.66,0:19:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.66,0:19:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.52,0:19:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是潤喉糖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.85,0:20:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案發前谷口先生給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.26,0:20:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子姐姐 交給妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.75,0:20:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官先生 你右手上的包裝紙是搶匪丟掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著搶匪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.57,0:20:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在谷口先生的西裝口袋裡摸索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.14,0:20:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是在找潤喉糖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.56,0:20:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概谷口先生和那個搶匪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.33,0:20:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天下午曾在某個地方碰面進行最終的籌劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.52,0:20:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為兩人那時都感冒了 喉嚨疼痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.36,0:20:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一個人把身上的潤喉糖一分為二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.66,0:20:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把一半給了另一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.72,0:20:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來搶匪闖入這裡後 喉嚨又痛起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.47,0:20:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想從口袋裡拿出潤喉糖的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.11,0:20:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻發現早已吃光了 只剩下包裝紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.54,0:20:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是搶匪想起谷口先生曾把潤喉糖放在西裝口袋裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.79,0:20:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想拿出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.46,0:20:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不知谷口先生之前已經把潤喉糖送給了柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.31,0:20:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.38,0:21:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩片潤喉糖包裝紙的切口完全吻合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.09,0:21:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.09,0:21:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅如此 谷口先生也好 那名搶匪也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.45,0:21:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩片潤喉糖包裝紙上都應該還留有他們的指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.17,0:21:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻拿去鑑定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.57,0:21:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷口先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.33,0:21:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼要反駁的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.42,0:21:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把潤喉糖給別人 還真是聰明呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.44,0:21:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因為借高利貸跟他認識的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.87,0:21:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了還債之後還可以花天酒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.35,0:21:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就策劃了這次搶劫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.66,0:21:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是早知道會變成這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.33,0:21:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會把潤喉糖送你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.23,0:23:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害 園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.40,0:23:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又讓妳解決了一件案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.86,0:23:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我都記不清了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.12,0:23:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這裡好像被針"噗"地刺了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.50,0:23:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"噗"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.92,0:23:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.57,0:23:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣一來 連新一也要甘拜下風了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.47,0:23:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後有我這又可愛又迷人的女高中生偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.65,0:23:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴木園子就夠啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.29,0:23:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.33,0:23:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不應該用她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.10,0:23:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要反省嘍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.21,0:23:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.42,0:23:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明先生 發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.20,0:23:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.34,0:24:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明先生是怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.45,0:24:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.08,0:24:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.71,0:24:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.25,0:24:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名門連續慘死事件(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.73,0:24:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.77,0:24:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西部名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.31,0:24:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次播出時間是10月20日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.19,0:24:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿風、阿龍跟葉月 你們要等我喔
